ai-patthana23.35:0.2_0: (These should be expanded as in the previous discourse.)
ai-patthana23.35:0.3_0: he should kinsmen, thinking: “There are skillful;”
ai-patthana23.35:1.1_0: But they don’t arisen in the teaching of the skillful, the support that has arisen in him.
ai-patthana23.35:1.1_1: Supported, supported by seven supports, and at six times.
ai-patthana23.35:2.1_0: But the truth of the teachings that has not arisen in the textual analysis of the meaning, the text, and the teaching has arisen.
ai-patthana23.35:3.1_0: But they haven’t declared the cause, what is the reason why those who have not arisen in the teaching.
ai-patthana23.35:4.1_0: But they haven’t heard what they have not been declared by the Buddha, for what has arisen, what has come to be.
ai-patthana23.35:5.1_0: You depend on what is the reason for seven years ...
ai-patthana23.35:6.1_0: shake off the sound of the past.
